    <section id="about" class="about-section-qrs345">
        <div class="container-bcd890">
            <h2 class="section-title-efg123">About OryvexToday</h2>
            <div class="about-content-tuv678">
                <div class="about-text-wxy901">
                    <p>OryvexToday has been transforming outdoor spaces since 2001, bringing innovative design and quality craftsmanship to every project. Our team of skilled professionals combines traditional building techniques with modern materials and technology.</p>
                    
                    <p>We believe that every outdoor space has potential to become something extraordinary. Whether you're looking to create an intimate gathering spot for family dinners or an expansive entertainment area for large gatherings, we have the expertise to make it happen.</p>
                    
                    <p>Our commitment to excellence extends beyond construction. We provide comprehensive support throughout the entire process, from initial consultation through project completion and beyond. Customer satisfaction is our top priority.</p>
                </div>
